{"type":"message","id":"f35caf70","parentId":"36abf942","timestamp":"2026-03-03T08:01:29.870Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我找到了Finnhub Market News工具。让我使用`finnhub.market.news.list.v1`来获取最新的市场新闻，这个工具stats成功率是100%，平均执行时间1.874ms。\n\n但是我注意到这个工具只返回新闻，没有热度(sentiment)指标。让我看看是否需要搜索其他工具来获取新闻热度。\n\n实际上，任务说的是\"热度≥80\"，这可能指的是新闻热度或者市场情绪。让我先执行这个新闻API看看返回什么数据，然后看看是否有热度字段。\n\n让我先获取search_id，然后执行。","thinkingSignature":"0f928c32fe54e9bdfb4f4a0fc2ab9f3d91f4b77b00a956d4dcc6fca755e77f4f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3fqubdqwd911_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace && node scripts/qveris_tool.mjs execute \"finnhub.market.news.list.v1\" --search-id \"acc68953-b3b7-4297-bbbf-8bcb90d36da3\" --params '{\"category\": \"general\"}'","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":12569,"output":206,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26759,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772524869697}}
