{"type":"message","id":"38fe4f6f","parentId":"d501ae81","timestamp":"2026-03-03T08:04:30.646Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"finnhub工具也有问题。让我看看之前成功执行的alternative_crypto_fear_greed_index工具是怎么调用的。也许是因为API结构不同。\n\n不过我注意到恐惧贪婪指数工具可以工作，而且当前值是14和20（都是恐惧状态，远低于80）。由于任务要求热度≥80才推送，而现在市场处于恐惧状态，没有达到阈值，所以我不需要推送任何消息给用户。\n\n让我确认一下，再检查一些其他可能的热度指标。也许我应该检查一下是否有其他\"热度\"相关的指标。但基于目前的数据，市场情绪明显处于恐惧状态（14-20远低于80），没有需要推送的高热度新闻。","thinkingSignature":"eeddb294ff0b7e21bbfcfa79f563216abfcef139b390231c4b7c682994a942c0"},{"type":"text","text":"让我再检查一下是否有其他可用的热度指标：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_64tf57jq3zkd_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace && node scripts/qveris_tool.mjs search \"trending stocks popular\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":24586,"output":193,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38763,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772525060952}}
